@startuml

skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor<<ServiceNow>> LightSkyBlue
  BackgroundColor<<OneDrive>> LightGreen
  BackgroundColor<<eBonding>> LightYellow
}

cloud "ServiceNow Cloud" <<ServiceNow>> {
  class ServiceNow {
    Incident
    Post Mortem
    Followup AI
    1) Create Incident in IMS
    2) Mitigate/Resolve Incident in IMS
    3) Create Post-Mortem
  }
}

cloud "Microsoft Azure Cloud" {
  class OneDrive <<OneDrive>> {
    ims_pm_onedrive
    1) Upload a document
    2) Download a document
    3) Share a document to users
  }
}

class eBonding <<eBonding>> {
  POST: /ims/create-post-mortem?incidentNo=IN3333
  response: attachment (MSWord docs)
  GET: /ims/parse-post-mortem?incidentNo=IN3333
  response: application/json
  PM-template.docx
}

ServiceNow -down-> OneDrive : Upload/Download/Share documents
ServiceNow -right-> eBonding : GS (Create Post-Mortem)

note right of eBonding
  POST: /ims/create-post-mortem?incidentNo=IN3333
  response: attachment (MSWord docs)
  GET: /ims/parse-post-mortem?incidentNo=IN3333
  response: application/json
end note

note right of ServiceNow
  Create Incident in IMS
  Mitigate/Resolve Incident in IMS
  Create Post-Mortem
end note

note left of OneDrive
  Upload a document
  Download a document
  Share a document to users
end note

@enduml
